It ended up what it is today something like the world’s rich failed state because it is trapped by the old vicious cycle of poverty and violence for so long that it came to think there was no other way. Still, It’s never too late to change the path we're on. The question, I think, is whether we Americans really understand all the history, and how it’s elements are connected.
